:'''Furdo:''' Wallace? Who is that? Is he a citizen who came to me for legal advice before? With all due respect, I need to see so many people every day... How could I remember each of their names?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} He's a Limestein.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301020334-->
