:'''Furdo:''' I've got a big case on my hands! It's a shame I'll never be the one to try the case...
:'''Furdo:''' I guess more specifically, I should say that there's no way this case can be tried... Even Lady Bronya herself would not be able to.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What's this case you're talking about?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Even Bronya can't handle it?
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027235-->
:'''Furdo:''' Yeah. Former Supreme Guardian Cocolia... passed during the Fragmentum disturbance that happened north of Belobog. Her daughter Bronya took over her position after that.
:'''Furdo:''' Lady Bronya stated that Cocolia went to the source of the Fragmentum and sacrificed herself to protect Belobog... But that's just what she is saying. Who knows what actually happened? There were no other witnesses after all...
:'''Furdo:''' ...Hmph. Then again, that all has nothing to do with me. Change is opportunity. All I have to do now is take hold of this opportunity and find a way to get myself seated at the court... I don't need to keep arguing with those old hags.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Here's to your success.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027239-->
::'''Furdo:''' Hopefully your words will bring me good luck... But I think my chances are not particularly good. Maybe Alexandra Plaza is just where I belong...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} You don't stand a chance.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501027241-->
::'''Furdo:''' You're right. There's no way it'll work out. Maybe Alexandra Plaza is just where I belong...
